&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We’re&amp;nbsp;excitedly seeking a Video Producer who has&amp;nbsp;a strong&amp;nbsp;team&amp;nbsp;mentality and experience in real estate media. The Video Producer will work with one of our top-producing teams in Atlanta and will&amp;nbsp;be responsible for&amp;nbsp;producing, editing, and delivering video property tours for their listings and social video content to amplify their personal brands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:17,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
